      "content": "but i only have one glass and i'm not even taking the pill at the exact same second as the juice. it's not like i'm drinking a whole gallon. surely a little bit won't actually do anything bad? it feels like a bit of an exaggeration to say it's \"dangerous\" for just a bit of juice.",
